ks, pour tahini sauce onto fish and serve warm or at room temperature. Garnish with pine nuts and chopped parsley."}],"hintsAndTricks":["Bitter orange juice can be replaced with a mixture of 50 g lemon juice and 100 g orange juice."],"basicInfo":["easy","10m","1h 15m","4 portions"]}